---

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="testimonials-header">
            <h2 class="testimonials-title">Lo que dicen quienes ya lo vivieron</h2>
            <div class="testimonials-divider"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-content">
                    <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9e8b7f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                        <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="testimonial-text">
                        "Un espacio para reconectar y encontrar claridad. La masterclass me ayudó a poner en perspectiva mis prioridades y me dio herramientas prácticas que uso todos los días."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">
                        <img src="/images/img_avatar_placeholder.jpg" alt="María Gómez" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2048%22%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20fill%3D%22%23e2e8f0%22%2F%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M24%2024c3.31%200%206-2.69%206-6s-2.69-6-6-6-6%202.69-6%206%202.69%206%206%206zm0%204c-4.42%200-8%203.58-8%208v2h16v-2c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z%22%20fill%3D%22%2394a3b8%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E'" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4 class="author-name">María Gómez</h4>
                        <span class="author-role">Profesional Independiente</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-content">
                    <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9e8b7f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                        <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="testimonial-text">
                        "Liliana tiene una forma única de transmitir calma y seguridad. Me llevé ejercicios muy valiosos para aplicar en mi rutina cuando siento que me desbordan las responsabilidades."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">
                        <img src="/images/img_avatar_placeholder.jpg" alt="Laura F." onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2048%22%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20fill%3D%22%23e2e8f0%22%2F%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M24%2024c3.31%200%206-2.69%206-6s-2.69-6-6-6-6%202.69-6%206%202.69%206%206%206zm0%204c-4.42%200-8%203.58-8%208v2h16v-2c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z%22%20fill%3D%22%2394a3b8%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E'" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4 class="author-name">Laura F.</h4>
                        <span class="author-role">Emprendedora</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-content">
                    <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9e8b7f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                        <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="testimonial-text">
                        "Fue un antes y un después. Venía en piloto automático y la masterclass me hizo frenar, observar y empezar a construir cambios reales y sostenibles en mi vida."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">
                        <img src="/images/img_avatar_placeholder.jpg" alt="Ana Rodríguez" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2048%22%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%2248%22%20height%3D%2248%22%20fill%3D%22%23e2e8f0%22%2F%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M24%2024c3.31%200%206-2.69%206-6s-2.69-6-6-6-6%202.69-6%206%202.69%206%206%206zm0%204c-4.42%200-8%203.58-8%208v2h16v-2c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z%22%20fill%3D%22%2394a3b8%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E'" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4 class="author-name">Ana Rodríguez</h4>
                        <span class="author-role">Directora de RRHH</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
